housands of companies in the americas and around the world among them are giants like boeing and nike as well as many smaller less wellknown firms our main business activities include international trade export import offshore domestic and countertrade marketing and distribution international project management trade financing and project financing transportation insurance and customs services natural resource development direct investment debt financing leasing and assetbased financing sojitz corporation of america manages operations in the us canada mexico and central and south america through our hemispherewide network of offices and our diverse array of group companies outside of the americas sojitz has a worldwide network of operating bases ready to do business back to top home sojitz corporation of america sca is the us subsidiary of sojitz corporation an integrated global trading  investment company with our regional headquarters in new york city we conduct business across the americas through our offices in argentina brazil canada mexico and peru more automotive energy food  agriculture aerospace  it metals  coal retail  lifestyle infrastructure  enviro chemicals industrial infrastructure  urban development sojitz group information sojitz group website グループのホームページ sojitz stock information sojitz worldwide network learn more sojitz wonderland sojitz news sojitz enters solar power business in chile new office in san jose ca fy  results april  to march  sojitz acquires stake in us power plant q financial results fy sojitz history doing business for over  years back to top business activities sojitz group activities in the americas aes merida iii s de rl de cv mexico    power generation business autrans corp us provider of subassemblies and justintime delivery services autrans de venezuela venezuela import and modularization of mitsubishi and hyundai assembly components central motriz sa guatemala car distributor fuji do brasil maquinas industriais ltda brazil s