corporation an integrated global trading company with  billion in annual trade transactions headquartered in tokyo sojitz has  offices  subsidiaries and   employees around the world  for over  years see full history sca has done business with trust reliability and results characteristics that are synonymous with the sojitz name main business activities include international trade export import offshore domestic and countertrade marketing and distribution international project management trade financing and project financing transportation insurance and customs services natural resource development direct investment debt financing leasing and assetbased financing through  business divisions sca has the ability to operate across an enormous scope of industries and sectors and to work with thousands of companies giants like boeing and nike in the americas  and around the world within the aerospace  it division of sca is the satcom department focusing on the satellite communications industry with concentration in the maritime government oilgas utilities and commercialenterprise market the satcom team has over  years of experience in satellite communications with unparalleled customer support new japan radio co njrc for over  years new japan radio co is the world class manufacturer of block up converters and low noise blockers for the satellite communications industry  with unparalleled engineering and breakthrough technology njrc has set the standards in quality durability and efficient vsat products in the industry njrc products are used globally across many satellite communications equipment including vsat terminals mobile communications marine radomes communicationsonthemove cotm aerospace and military manpacks  engineers who knows the industry knows that njrc is the name for top performance and long lasting equipment back to top leadership leadership a message from the ceo of sojitz corporation of america sojitz corporation of america has remained successful for over  years by providing knowledge speed and networking to our trading and investment  business activities we continue to expand and diversify our business model in the fastpaced and rapidly changing modern era based in new york and on my second assignment in the united states i am excited to  lead the expansion of business in such a dynamic region such as the americas our guiding principles are to conduct business with trust speed and perseverance while innovating to take on new challenges the long and close relationships we’ve built with business partners around the world are proof that these principles have stood the test of time sojitz’s greatest asset our employees adhere to these timehonored tenets while continually bringing “new way new value” to the americas region   back to top offices us offices sojitz corporation of america headquarters new york city  avenue of the americas fl new york ny  usa tel fax sojitz corporation of america washington dc branch  eye street nw suite  washington dc  usa tel fax sojitz corporation of america houston branch  west loop south suite  houston texas  usa tel fax sojitz corporation of america portland branch  sw fifth avenue pacwest center suite  portland oregon  usa tel fax sojitz corporation of america seattle branch  th avenue suite  seattle washington  usa tel fax sojitz corporation of america mesa office  satellite of seattle branch  n greenfield rd bldg  suite  mesa az  usa tel  fax  sojitz corporation of america san jose office  metro drive suite  san jose ca  tel  argentina office sojitz argentina sa av corrientes  piso   buenos aires argentina tel fax brazil offices sojitz do brasil sa av paulista  – torre norte – o andar cep  sao paulo brasil tel fax url httpwwwsojitzbrcomsiteenglishindexhtm sojitz do brasil sa rio de janeiro branch praia do flamengo  andar edificio international rio flamengo rio de janeiro rj cep  brasil tel fax canada offices sojitz canada corporation headquarters vancouver box  two bentall centre s